1.1
log
@Add a port for DateTime::Locale. From DESCR:

DateTime::Locale is primarily a factory for the various locale
subclasses. It also provides some functions for getting information on
all the available locales.
@
text
@# $MirOS: ports/infrastructure/templates/perlmod.Makefile,v 1.2 2009/01/04 17:20:07 bsiegert Exp $

COMMENT=		localization support for DateTime.pm
DISTNAME=		DateTime-Locale-0.42
